OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FWords by Sophia Ankel, ITV News
OL,8,FIt is a heartbreaking scene: Doctors
OL,9,Fare frantically working over the limp
OL,10,Fbody of a four-year-old girl lying on
OL,11,Fa metal trolley in one of Mariupol's
OL,12,Flast-remaining hospitals.
OL,14,FThe girl - her body pale and lifeless
OL,15,F- was in her home when it was struck
OL,16,Fby a missile in the first week of
OL,17,FRussia's full-scale invasion of
OL,18,FUkraine in 2022.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/13
