OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FDespite the medical teams' best
OL,7,Fefforts to save her, four-year-old
OL,8,FYevanhelina died.
OL,10,FUkrainian A&E nurse Olena Olkhovska is
OL,11,Ffilmed as she cries over her body.
OL,13,FThe tragic scene is featured in the
OL,14,Feyewitness documentary filmed by
OL,15,FAssociated Press journalist Mtsyslav
OL,16,FChernov during the siege of the
OL,17,FUkrainian city by the Russian army.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/13
