OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News exclusively from
OL,7,Fher new home in the eastern city of
OL,8,FDnipro, Olena says the death of the
OL,9,Ffour-year-old girl was a "turning
OL,10,Fpoint" for the team of doctors
OL,11,FMariupol Regional Hospital.
OL,13,FThey were used to treating adult
OL,14,Fpatients in emergency situations - but
OL,15,Fchildren with shrapnel wounds and
OL,16,Fmissing limps was new territory for
OL,17,Fthem.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/13
