OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,F"There was no water, no electricity,
OL,7,Fno communication. We were like in a
OL,8,Ftrance," she said, adding that they
OL,9,Fonly charged their phones to use their
OL,10,Fflashlights during operations.
OL,12,FOne day, the team raided a nearby
OL,13,Fpharmacy to stock up on equipment.
OL,14,FWhen it snowed, they collected snow
OL,15,Finto containers and melted it so they
OL,16,F"could at least wash our hands" before
OL,17,Fmedical procedures.
OL,19,FOlena said she constantly thought
OL,20,Fabout evacuating her family but that
OL,21,Fthey "didn't have the opportunity" to.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/13
