OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the journalists with them
OL,7,Fkept filming and feeding footage back
OL,8,Fto the outside world. Families of
OL,9,Fdoctors in the hospital later told
OL,10,FOlena how relieved they were to see
OL,11,Fthem all alive.
OL,13,FOn March 12, the Russians encircled
OL,14,Fthe hospital. Ten of them came in with
OL,15,Fmachine guns looking for Ukrainian
OL,16,Fsoldiers.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/13
