OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FTwenty-five tense Russian checkpoints
OL,7,Flater, they were out. Her only thought
OL,8,F- "I want to wish that other people
OL,9,Fnever experience something like this."
OL,11,FThe Oscar nomination is a first for
OL,12,FUkrainian cinema, and for a film that
OL,13,Fdocumented the horrors of the war at
OL,14,Fits peak. It has reminded viewers of
OL,15,Fthe catastrophic scenes civilians were
OL,16,Ffaced with.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/13
