OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FOlena said: "This documentary is a
OL,7,Fmust-see so that people don't
OL,8,Fexperience what we experienced there.
OL,9,FIt is incomprehensible. It is
OL,10,Fimpossible to understand how this
OL,11,Fcould happen in the 21st century."
OL,13,FToday, she lives in rented
OL,14,Faccommodation in Dnipro - and is still
OL,15,Fworking in a hospital.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/13
